channel.title: Looking for someone that knows the packet protocol of a 600+ client
channel.description:
hi, i am looking for someone (preferably a programmer type, no specific language experience needed) that has a continuing interest in private servers. additionally, they need to be knowledgeable about any 600+ revisions packet structure and the client in general. primarily because i have zero knowledge of any 600+ clients.
experience with Linux is also nice if you have it
anyone that can fill these requirements please PM me, thanks
